<h1 itemprop="headline"> Arts and Technology Academy of Pontiac</h1></header><div itemprop="articleBody">
<div class="clearfix">
<div class="sixcol first">
<p class="slogan uppercase bold">Providing every student a personalized learning experience!</p>
<p><a href="http://atappontiac.com/">atappontiac.com</a></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pre-K to 12th Grade</span></p>
<p>Academy of Arts and Technology of Pontiac<br> 888 Enterprise Drive<br> Pontiac, MI. 48341<br> Phone: <a href="tel:1-248-452-9309">248.452.9309</a></p>
</div>
<div class="sixcol last"><p><iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2935.896036925328!2d-83.25404398486826!3d42.62116082656562!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x8824bf7b8c44f99f%3A0x510f4966e11afe89!2s888+Enterprise+Dr%2C+Pontiac%2C+MI+48341!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1522087263056" width="400" height="300" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p></div>
</div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Arts and Technology Academy of Pontiac (ATAP) is located in a newer facility that has been designed specifically for the students’ and teachers’ needs. ATAP is committed to providing every student a personalized learning experience and the guidance they need to be successful. Students at the academy are mentored and guided by dedicated staff to  develop a passion for learning utilizing a well-rounded curriculum that includes art, music, drama, and foreign language.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Unique Qualities of ATAP</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Small, Caring, Nurturing Environment</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Music, Gym, Drama, Dance and Art Classes</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Technology Integrated Curriculum</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Positive Behavior Support</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Personalized Student Achievement Plans for all students</span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
</div></article></section></main><footer id="footer"><div class="clearfix">
